{"tid":1224960,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"不如出年立法會選舉，泛民本土各派大和解","createTime":"2019-06-15T05:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T13:03:52.000Z","uid":82555,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f934c98f69835c9727a2064fb939da9e73f3d74b","tid":1224960,"uid":82555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:43:41.000Z","msg":"集中所有非建制派既力量，每個選區只派一張名單出選，而每張名單都有咁多個黨派既人，而名單既順序可以而家開始傾，反正距離下次立法會選舉仲有一年時間，慢慢傾就應該可以傾到一個大家都滿意既result<br />\n始終建制派咁團結，你無得同佢玩<br />\n我地只能夠集中大家既力量，團結一致，務求重奪立法會過半議席，咁先可以有效監察政府<br />\n可能係某部分議題上，泛民可能會出賣選民，但總好過而家比政府禁住黎打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外，係功能組別上，每年其實都有一部分功能組別係自動當選，其實有無方法係個d選區派到人出選？我地唔一定贏到，但至少係個個界別可以引入競爭，比到d壓力建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然未必可以做到好似美國咁得民主共和兩個黨，但我覺得如果做到好似台灣藍綠咁樣，至少可以弱化政府既管治<br />\nsorry 1999，因為我本人唔係讀政治，所以觀點可能有d理想化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1163932ee95455e103112bfb4b2b0e8ec0b9358f","tid":1224960,"uid":173852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不抱希望性支持<br />\n依幾年可以睇到無左議會否決權有幾恐怖"},{"pid":"ecdbb143af1b3114d232519df7680889f15bf758","tid":1224960,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:12:30.000Z","msg":"小心五毛分化，敵人係建制<br />\n<br />\n03之後反共派拎半數令多數政府法案無法通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f15a9df099f2422bf0eec083239d76d8263767","tid":1224960,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:13:02.000Z","msg":"仍需求大量選民登記表格<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家去影印時可以淨印頭兩板！<br />\n<br />\n大家可以今晚係美孚交低選民登記表比我或者聽日自發咁去派<br />\n<br />\n現時已安排足夠人手於維園入口set站派表<br />\n需要大家沿路同於終點繼續派<br />\n感激大家！ <br />\n<br />\n選民登記表格link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=c8530d64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<br />\nTG GROUP: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DFZtbBYpgyLP_AFD8epM3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDFZtbBYpgyLP_AFD8epM3A&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=0db2a9d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DFZtbBYpgyLP_AFD8epM3A</a>"},{"pid":"0e9b336004e87a25dce4167f7479f758bf58dab9","tid":1224960,"uid":82555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1163932ee95455e103112bfb4b2b0e8ec0b9358f","tid":1224960,"uid":173852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不抱希望性支持<br />\n依幾年可以睇到無左議會否決權有幾恐怖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:34:28.000Z","msg":"如果泛民本土各派，能夠借今次事件，團結一致，1對1硬砍建制，除左可以減少分薄票源，仲可以團結到所有反建制既力量，制衡政府<br />\n<br />\n見連登既5毛開始鬧鄺神係鬼，分化大家，就知佢地好驚反建制既勢力團結一致<br />\n<br />\n希望佢地可以吸收呢次教訓，統合各方反建制勢力，係黎緊立法會選舉贏返次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畢竟，留俾香港既時間已經唔多，50年都差唔多過左一半"},{"pid":"a2dc00874e37d60243103150ce2bff13dd3dc156","tid":1224960,"uid":140915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:35:17.000Z","msg":"大家由得呢個post沉，免得分散注意力。"},{"pid":"0df02936ed81643255ee1b8a4dc0e7551ac53839","tid":1224960,"uid":80303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"純粹講返技術問題，大家都係專注返反送終<br />\n<br />\n依個係政府仆街位，現實好難咁做<br />\n香港立法會個選舉制叫黑爾數額<br />\n即係每張名單，理論上每有x票，就可以分到一席，如果你有2x票，就有2席，etc<br />\n<br />\n但現實上，只有好少名單會夠一席既票數。當所有名單都冇x票時，就會由最高票名單開始，一張名單一席咁送出去。<br />\n<br />\n假設有4席，黑爾數額係10000票，民主名單就要有40000票，先攞到4席<br />\n但建制利用上面個送議席原理，做4張名單，一張5000票，票張4000票etc,一樣可以攞到4席<br />\n<br />\n所以依個方案係票效上好差，亦係點解會拆名單的原因<br />\n<br />\n但亦正因為咁，民主派內鬥好嚴重"},{"pid":"9f7de3827f22489ee8fe9e8c3ea968d863b7db93","tid":1224960,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:03:52.000Z","msg":"每區都有&rsquo;代表本土利益&lsquo;既人<br />\n就唔使有和解問題<br />\n唔使嘈 白票 vs 飯民 之類問題<br />\n<br />\n不如盡力支持素人參選好過"}]}